    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy the ride! This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels just like it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it tucked away in the garage, and stayed on top of every single service. It drives like a total dream and is ready for its next adventure. You\u2019ve gotta see it in person to really see how flawless it is!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
