      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3, meticulously maintained to preserve its analog purity. At its heart is the S54B32 straight-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a double-VANOS variable valve timing system that has been fully serviced. This example features the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, delivering power to the rear wheels via a factory-spec variable M differential lock. Crucially, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the rod bearings have been replaced as a preventative measure. The suspension geometry remains precise with refreshed bushings and original dampers. The exterior retains its factory depth and gloss, while the interior leather shows no bolster wear or UV damage. This is a turn-key specimen for the discerning collector who demands mechanical perfection and chassis rigidity.",
